	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">Deadline</h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>The director had called the group together in our largest consult space; he placed his huge scaly hands on the edges of the podium and deliberately cleared both throats.</p>
<p>‚ÄúThe Steering Committee insists that we ship the XN24 this cycle ‚Äì and a committee directive is binding on us all.‚Äù</p>
<p>The silence was only broken by the Subspace Team‚Äôs stuttering giggle-squeaks: an involuntary stress reaction among the Aratoi. The director swivelled three eyes to glare at them: ‚ÄúYou lot mislabelled Outcome References 22 to 86 as ‚Äòfailure to return from subspace‚Äô instead of ‚Äòpilot navigation error‚Äô. Are you trying to get me fired?‚Äù</p>
<p>The head of the Thrust Team limped to the front, his carapace still blackened from the testing incident, and said, ‚ÄúIt is impossible, Sir. Did you not tell them about our thrust tests?‚Äù</p>
<p>The director‚Äôs claws slowly extended and retracted before he spoke: ‚ÄúUnfortunately all engineering and design specialists have been removed from the Steering Committee in order to streamline the product-to-market process. So<em> I </em>never told them &#8211; but they have handed down policy regarding <em>that</em> incident.‚Äù He read directly from a clipboard hovering nearby: ‚ÄúDue to the cost in equipment and danger to key personnel all future thrust testing will be executed in simulation only ‚Äì associated danger or injury related pay or benefits will be retroactively adjusted.‚Äù</p>
<p>Timidly the new intern raised a vivid orange pseudo-tentacle:  ‚ÄúExcuse me Sir, but you must be aware that the design hasn&#8217;t been approved by Galactic Standards yet.‚Äù<br />
‚ÄúI thought your clan-twin worked there: that‚Äôs why you work here.‚Äù<br />
‚ÄúBut sir, she can&#8217;t sign off on plans she doesn&#8217;t have!‚Äù<br />
‚ÄúI think, for the sake of her clan-twin‚Äôs future, she should trust to our expertise. After all, the steering committee has declared the XN24 ready to ship!‚Äù</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	
	<footer class="entry-footer">
